Application Name: MWP Museum of Art Mobile Guide.
Number of Reviews: .
Application Description: The mobile guide is an exciting way to enhance your MWPAI Museum of Art experience with multimedia tours, audio and video podcasts, and details about the artworks and exhibitions. The Patron, Artist, Muse: Women of MWP tour highlights artworks across the Museum’s collection through the women who were instrumental in founding the Institute (patrons), women who inspired artists’ creativity (muses), and women who created a great number of works in the Museum’s collection (artists)Read moreCollapse.
